  "remarks": "Prom Composite LLC is a Russian company developing and producing unmanned aerial vehicles (UAVs). Its portfolio includes UAV models such as UAV-KT “Lisa”, UAV-KT “Volk”, first-person view (FPV) UAV “Dozor” and FPV UAV “Vespa”, as well as large radar domes. Those products support both civilian and military applications, reflecting Prom Composite LLC’s dual-use profile.",
